## ğŸ› ï¸ CLI Commands

```bash
# Create new project
pyos new myos

# Build OS
pyos build main.py -o myos.iso

# Run in QEMU
pyos run myos.iso

# Debug mode
pyos debug myos.iso

# Generate Assembly only
pyos asm main.py -o kernel.asm

# Check dependencies
pyos check
```

